<A>__{bloom fishes a crumpled piece of paper from his pocket and thrusts it in front of stephen's face. on it are written dozens of variations in stylized fonts of "penelope the smuggler."}
<C>__{bloom }
<D>__{she's been singing the smuggler song since athens.}
